      "message": "Now that DefaultTarget is called A LOT more often, it would be better to get rid of defaultTargetLock and .Clone() and instead use atomic.Value and clone in \u0027SetDefaultTarget\u0027. Roughly:\n\nfunc (s ...) SetDefaultTarget(t ...) {\n  s.defaultTarget.Store(t.Clone())\n}\n\nfunc (s ...) DefaultTarget() ... {\n  return s.defaultTarget().Clone()\n}\n\n// Return value of defaultTarget MUST not be mutated.\nfunc (s ...) defaultTarget() types.Target {\n  return s.defaultTarget.Load().(types.Target)\n}\n\nfunc (s ...) findTarget(...) types.Target {\n  dt :\u003d s.defaultTarget()\n\n  ...\n}",
